headline: Why Is The Trade Desk (TTD) Stock Soaring Today
summary: Shares of digital advertising platform The Trade Desk (NASDAQ:TTD) jumped 5.1% in the morning session after the stock extended its positive momentum as the company provided an upbeat statement regarding its partnership with Walmart.
